{"tid":2164770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★深圳地鐵10號線設「華為站」　乘客爭相用 iPhone打卡拍照","createTime":"2020-08-19T11:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T08:18:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":627,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"b3fc345ad6e25cbdacdbb47b39a5134300cdaeb5","tid":2164770,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200819/photo/bkn-20200819183327271-0819_00952_001_02b.jpg?20200819183324\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200819%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200819183327271-0819_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20200819183324&h=05e45b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳地鐵10號線周二（18日）啟用，是深圳首批擁有5G網絡全覆蓋的地鐵線，起於福田口岸站，途經福田區、龍崗區，止於雙擁街站，線路全長29.3公里，設有24個站，當中最受注的是「華為站」，引來不少民眾拍照打卡。<br />\n<br />\n網傳照片所有，乘客舉起不同品牌的手機在月台與「華為站」拍照，大多為國產手機，有華為旗下榮耀手機，亦有蘋果iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200819/bkn-20200819183327271-0819_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200819%2Fbkn-20200819183327271-0819_00952_001.html&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=9158f6b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200819/bkn-20200819183327271-0819_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"38e0bbdf8c8485399d044cb2da0377652db6c1b1","tid":2164770,"uid":19454,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef7e5ba291d1d615854eb3b11bcac46d0fec1f4","tid":2164770,"uid":19454,"like":385,"dislike":3,"scor