es/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d46d6666ed167b1307cbe44d3cb2abc0005daad","tid":2164770,"uid":326881,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:11:38.000Z","msg":"深圳人一年後經過這個車站，難免感到失落。國家怎麼就不爭氣呢？給了華為這麼長時間，為什麼就不能自主研發些什麼呢？<br />\n<br />\n深圳人兩年後再經過這個車站，看著上面醒目的大字，「華為」就是個笑話。<br />\n<br />\n深圳人三年後再經過這個車站，華為倒閉了，車站也改名了。<br />\n<br />\n深圳人心裡嘀咕，這車站名字應該改成「化為」，化為烏有的化為。他想起三年前新車站落成時，自己和親友爭相打卡的愛國熱情，不盡失聲笑了出來。再看看四周的監控鏡頭，他暗暗僥倖並沒有說出心中那句「草泥馬B，化為」。"},{"pid":"98852562aaec8cb6ef2ba966377efe11438c7004","tid":2164770,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d270f09baeac968973741b9c44a6b7d67607cb68","tid":2164770,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80807510eaf93bfef2ec41beec446daf21e07ecb","tid":2164770,"uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"講真，大陸真係少人用華為，白粉張圖真係做假嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"我唔敢話少<br />\n但比得起錢既都prefer蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c79530ad6719ffb8d5f60e616ff23746936005c","tid":2164770,"uid":129340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a31452ca58e3b6535deb95e8a69b4f2a39515bd","tid":2164770,"uid":12628,"like":86,"dislike":3,"score":83,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"用前鏡影咁跳脫<span class=\"xx-large\">🥴</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:14:07.000Z","msg":"中間air pod 係咩事？"},{"pid":"550914977e4b3057233e180c0119c25b050fdf77","tid":2164770,"uid":21995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:15:18.000Z","msg":"屎畏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla